## 🧠 Skill Routing

When the request matches, read and follow the SKILL.md from `.trae/skills/` **before** answering:

| Request | Skill |
|---|---|
| Product ideas, brainstorming | `.trae/skills/gstack-office-hours` |
| Plan review, strategy | `.trae/skills/gstack-ceo-review` |
| Code review, security check | `.trae/skills/gstack-review` |
| Bugs, edge cases, testing | `.trae/skills/gstack-qa` |
| Research, compare libraries | `.trae/skills/gstack-browse` |
| Feature spec, "build from scratch" | `.trae/skills/gsd-spec` |
| Context rot, "what's the progress" | `.trae/skills/gsd-state` |
| Root cause analysis | `.trae/skills/superpowers-debugging` |
| UX flow, screen-by-screen API docs | `.trae/skills/ux-flow-api-docs` |
| API design, Mongoose modeling | `.trae/skills/api-design` / `.trae/skills/nosql-database-design` |

