## 🔁 Workflows

For multi-step tasks, read and execute the workflow from `.agent/workflows/`:

| Trigger | Workflow |
|---|---|
| New feature or module | `.agent/workflows/feature-implementation.md` |
| Bug / error / broken behavior | `.agent/workflows/bug-fix.md` |
| Code review request | `.agent/workflows/code-review.md` |
| API audit / Postman sync | `.agent/workflows/api-audit.md` |
